Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:03.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:07.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}憎しみに　変わっていく前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:09.78,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}何もかもそうだろ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:14.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.87,0:01:17.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:19.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:23.92,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:28.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:35.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}壊しあって　解り合ってたことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:37.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:41.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:45.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:51.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:56.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:02:03.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:06.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:10.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君はつぶやいて　信じる事が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:13.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:15.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:19.36,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:24.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}本当の愛を知るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:03.20,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛因愛而愈加沉重 卻拒絕理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.20,0:01:07.68,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在愛變為恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:09.78,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}所有一切皆是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:14.83,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}窘迫的永遠是這眼前的迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.84,0:01:17.65,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}彷彿被吞噬之物的寫實
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:19.96,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在這被扭曲的進退兩難之時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:23.92,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使海誓山盟的兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:28.27,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也漸行著冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.94,0:01:35.70,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}毀滅與理解之物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.77,0:01:37.55,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}早已被遺棄
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:41.08,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}這難道是滅亡之盡頭？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.10,0:01:45.47,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}否認這一切 挺身面對之時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:51.87,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即將殞落之時 都不會逃離眼前的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.90,0:01:56.54,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}啊，無論如何也要找尋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.58,0:02:03.22,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}你的雙眸 雙手的溫存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.34,0:02:06.73,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}說什麼「愛總是只給我帶來傷害」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.75,0:02:10.40,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君之低聲細語 深信之言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.42,0:02:13.40,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}是在恐懼中哭泣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:15.55,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}認識著軟弱 渴望著堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:19.36,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}當不再恐懼而滿懷信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:24.16,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}那將是真實的愛
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:29.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}純真さが シンプルな力に 変わる 世界に影をつくりだす
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:44.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ガラスケ一スに横たわる 光の存在に触れたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:51.44,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}振り上げた手 降ろせなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:22:00.11,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちるようにしゃがみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:08.43,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 明日の理想だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.67,0:22:15.92,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}語り継ぐような 美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:23.25,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}この体を失いそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:32.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ギリギリの場所が 哀しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.38,0:21:29.80,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}當純真變為單純的力量 世界由此誕生了影子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:44.34,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}穿透過玻璃櫥 感觸著這光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:51.44,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}舉起的手無法放下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:22:00.11,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}卻如同墜落般跌下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:08.43,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 拋開明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.67,0:22:15.92,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即便無法成為傳承的美談
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.13,0:22:23.25,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}如同就要失去這副身軀一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.45,0:22:32.42,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在極限的邊緣 跌入悲傷的深淵
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機正向本艦接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.01,0:00:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.53,0:00:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打! 攻擊了!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.11,0:00:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在幹嘛!? 打!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.74,0:00:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人的話 和你們就一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了!? 快點!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥的話 又會有無辜的人們受到傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.38,0:00:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別 別過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.40,0:00:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子們也是你們造成的犧牲者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.09,0:00:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:29.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太靠前了 准尉 保持距離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.60,0:00:46.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.33,0:00:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下不了手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.50,0:00:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.90,0:02:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒勁的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留手了麼 還是想羞辱我麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.46,0:02:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧 瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.88,0:02:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我啊 阿雷魯亞啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是 超兵!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.18,0:02:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam 超度你吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪 瑪麗!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.98,0:03:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有這種水平
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再放手了 瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.43,0:03:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過載?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.45,0:03:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可憐啊 機體沒有處在萬全的狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也就沒有砍的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機 包圍那架有兩部推進的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.36,0:04:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.64,0:04:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.42,0:04:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twin Drive…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam全體後退
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪·李·諾莉艾卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要切斷敵人的聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.39,0:04:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過魚雷散佈高濃度粒子和煙霧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.45,0:04:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 煙霧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目視通信被…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.82,0:04:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交戰空域被濃煙覆蓋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子量增大 和MS隊的通信被隔絕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到現在才改變戰術?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要重整陣形 發出撤退信號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.16,0:04:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.74,0:05:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:04.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.33,0:05:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法捕捉到機體Arios
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞他…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.62,0:05:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.65,0:05:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有Arios的反應?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.78,0:05:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.67,0:05:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過任務記錄確定Arios的交戰地點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.99,0:05:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO的收容結束後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee和Cherudim去搜索Arios
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道 無論怎麼說 你太獨斷專行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風太大 我聽不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.81,0:05:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮瑞斯中尉的Ahead丟失了?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即組織搜索班
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這要怎樣向斯米盧諾夫大佐交待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子沒有追兵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者幫我們把A-LAWS引開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.78,0:06:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別…別這樣 瑪麗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是沒有MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能對付你這個瑕疵品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.16,0:06:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.01,0:06:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗! 瑪麗·帕法西!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗 瑪麗 瑪麗 瑪麗 瑪麗!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.45,0:06:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.11,0:06:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷…魯亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.74,0:06:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗 我的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:06:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷…魯亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗 瑪麗 瑪麗·帕法西!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.13,0:07:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 再怎麼說也不用您親自去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.21,0:07:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離我遠一點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.15,0:07:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據記錄裡的資料 應該是在這片區域
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的腦量子波是這麼感覺的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心中正在哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊中尉的 都是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸艦命令?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停止中尉搜索!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是上面的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的部隊要專注於攻擊天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.86,0:07:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉的搜索就交給正規軍好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim已經出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee到達彈射甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞 Arios的交戰空域已經傳送完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.14,0:08:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡量避免與A-LAWS的戰鬥 專注於搜索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:13.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞·愛德 出發
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee已經出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.82,0:08:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即進入潛航準備
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 我說過不要使用TRANS-AM吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.91,0:08:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然TWIN DRIVE還在能運轉狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修理拜託了 哈雷魯亞他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.01,0:08:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈·庫洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.98,0:08:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣好嗎 你來維修Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.65,0:08:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在KARARON的人們平安脫離前 我什麼都可以做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.09,0:08:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…阿雷魯亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:08:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…阿雷魯亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.54,0:09:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…阿雷魯亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於 睜開眼睛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.65,0:09:26.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去檢查了一下機體
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是兩邊的系統都當機了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.11,0:09:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑我們看來是修不好的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.60,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救援能來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能問個問題麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:40.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會是索瑪·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想恐怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.09,0:09:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被植入了另一個人格
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以此來讓失去的五感復原吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人機關 把我作為超兵送到軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.54,0:09:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從而讓組織的存在得以延續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等卑劣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧如此 才能第一次見到你的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且馬上明白了就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.75,0:10:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是多虧了腦量子波吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠這樣子和你交談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 想都沒想過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.71,0:10:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 也讓我問一問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼過來的? 自從逃出超人機關之後
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.69,0:10:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了逃避處分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和同伴一起從設施裡逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於沒有帶你一起逃走這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.45,0:10:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初我很後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 幸好沒那麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和同伴一起奪取了運輸船 從殖民衛星逃了出去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:01.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒有一點目的地…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.95,0:11:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就那麼持續著漂流
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於艦內的糧食和空氣都見底了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.03,0:11:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 我不想死!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.72,0:11:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.42,0:11:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 我的名字是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.69,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你的身體裡 有著另一個人格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不能作為借口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.19,0:11:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷魯亞就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.42,0:11:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一活了下來的我 詛咒著命運
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒著超人機關…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒著這個世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要改變世界 才接受成為Gundam機師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.59,0:11:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為超兵能做的事情就只有戰鬥了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.68,0:11:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪·皮瑞斯那時的記憶怎樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在的 她的人格也在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就明白的吧? 我所做過的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.41,0:12:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.97,0:12:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把同伴 把同胞們 用這雙手…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩次奪去了大家的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.12,0:12:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾經殺掉過你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那個時候的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.07,0:12:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把另一個你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把哈雷魯亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.45,0:12:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留下這個傷痕也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是索瑪·皮瑞斯…!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你一樣 皮瑞斯就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 該怎麼辦才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了索瑪·皮瑞斯就是瑪麗之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我腦子裡就全都是你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要把你救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 實現了願望的現在 該怎麼辦才好…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的我 能給你的東西實在是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你陪在這裡 我就很開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 終於能夠遇到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有五感 只能用腦量子波呼喊的我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你做出了回應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你 我才能夠感謝活著這件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.74,0:13:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的你 現在能這樣注視著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.65,0:13:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠交談 甚至能夠觸摸到…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.99,0:13:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種時刻竟然會來臨…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.48,0:13:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:48.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 感謝您…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.30,0:13:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Allelujah
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.68,0:13:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦軍?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那機體是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.21,0:14:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認識的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 那聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.48,0:14:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 集中到中央區域去!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.92,0:14:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年輕… 男子的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那個時候的Gundam駕駛員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從中尉身邊離開 你這天行者!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.24,0:14:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了啊 克勞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在抱歉 第3支部被敵人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在為能夠再會而欣喜就好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.32,0:14:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個 聯邦政府終於對中東下手了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.26,0:14:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遭受了襲擊的阿扎帝斯坦被正規軍駐入
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎樹立了臨時政權
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨時政權…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.32,0:14:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 瑪麗娜·伊斯瑪依露大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎 阿扎帝斯坦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 都是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.09,0:15:06.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯邦政府想要以臨時政權為中心解體各國
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.49,0:15:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重組中東…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.72,0:15:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解體… 重組中東…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.16,0:15:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎帝斯坦王國已經不存在了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.20,0:15:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.73,0:15:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎帝斯坦竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.80,0:15:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把人格全部覆蓋重寫?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 現在的我並不是索瑪·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.83,0:15:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗·帕法茜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是中尉真正的名字麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超人機關竟然做到這個地步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.28,0:15:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗是溫柔的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.46,0:15:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是回去殺害他人的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.90,0:16:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會把瑪麗交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:03.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是回到聯邦和A-LAWS的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.08,0:16:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她又會被作為超兵對待的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你是天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.41,0:16:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算和你在一起中尉還是會被捲入戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.28,0:16:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會做那種事!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.39,0:16:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有愚蠢到會去相信恐怖分子說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.68,0:16:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請相信我!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.97,0:16:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我由於你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.50,0:16:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你們愚蠢的行動失去了很多同胞和部下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.36,0:16:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份憎恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能會忘記!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:32.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要這樣 大佐!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就請開槍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.16,0:16:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為交換 請把瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.62,0:16:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請發誓再也不會把索瑪·皮瑞斯捲入戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼 阿雷魯亞?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能夠幸福地活下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.18,0:16:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請開槍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.79,0:16:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悉從尊意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.84,0:16:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.94,0:17:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.17,0:17:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大 大佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在剛才 索瑪·皮瑞斯中尉光榮戰死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了向上層部報告 我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.72,0:17:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.13,0:17:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來還沒有道過謝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.11,0:17:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5年前 低軌道空間站的事故
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.65,0:17:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對能來參加救援活動一事 表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米盧諾夫大佐!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.11,0:17:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只徵用索瑪·皮瑞斯進行對Gundam戰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而沒有讓她參加其他戰爭的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很感謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種措辭 果然不是我所認識的中尉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 我身體中的索瑪·皮瑞斯是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要成為…您的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.84,0:18:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那句話就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.90,0:18:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐～!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要活著… 要活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他一起 獲得幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都非常感謝您了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.50,0:18:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由超人機關技術研究所派遣而來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:18:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超兵1號 索瑪·皮瑞斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年紀這麼小…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tieren Taozi…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的MS…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對Gundam的王牌麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她還只是個小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.29,0:19:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉是第一次品味到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 所謂勝利的美酒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.12,0:19:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是 勝利的美酒…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.25,0:19:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼!? 別來管我!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.88,0:19:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去戰鬥 少尉!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.20,0:19:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.18,0:19:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐要是不在了的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就變成獨自一人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.49,0:20:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.95,0:20:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 還活在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:19.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 給予了這樣的我生存的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.98,0:20:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.84,0:20:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落到海裡的話想找也沒轍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機接近 敵機接近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.49,0:20:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.66,0:20:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用光通信?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮瑞斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.94,0:21:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞發現 阿雷魯亞發現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.58,0:21:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓別人一頓好找結果在這裡泡馬子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.73,0:21:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 挺有一手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.33,0:22:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅傳來的通信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.40,0:22:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到哈普狄斯姆了的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞 找到了!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.96,0:22:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也 會笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.29,0:22:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有開心的事的話 誰都會笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.27,0:23:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.58,0:23:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是太好了啊 阿雷魯亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的戰鬥理由也還沒有失去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.86,0:23:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦 好像跟女朋友在一起的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.13,0:23:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女 女朋友!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.99,0:23:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.38,0:23:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子到底在幹什麼啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣麼 找到阿雷魯亞·哈普狄斯姆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.25,0:23:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是好消息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.29,0:23:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.94,0:23:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會知道我在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.92,0:23:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是同類所以知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.82,0:23:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.52,0:23:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 和我的容貌一模一樣?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.92,0:23:43.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為DNA也是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.70,0:23:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹼基序列模式 0988TYPE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.61,0:23:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.97,0:23:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.71,0:23:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡傑諾·瑞婕塔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.13,0:23:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視者…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.94,0:24:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞·愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡本斯·阿爾馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.30,0:24:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個革新的存在終於對面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.46,0:24:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 無暇的歪曲
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.40,0:24:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞計劃的腳步 漸漸加快


